outputs.output_descr: Continuation of development of an Iraqi National Humanitarian Mine Action Organisation in Southern Iraq capable of conducting Mine Action activities independently. funded by the Iraq Trust fund (A7-05) and AusAid.

Output in Interim Country Strategy 09-10: Non-governmental institutions strengthened to undertake demining and provide assistance to the victims of landmines and explosive remnants of war in an effective manner.

Supoprt is provided to the developemnt of a national humanitarian mine action organisation, to enable it to independantly conduct clearance and mine risk education in the most vulnerable communities in the south of Iraq, therefor promoting rural and agricutlural development.

project_descr: Development of an Iraqi National Humanitarian Mine Action Organisation in Southern Iraq capable of  independently conducting Mine Action activities in support of agricultural development.
project_title: Development  of a National Mine Action Organisation
